'''Israyil''' d tamurt tezga-g g umenẓaw n asya, g [[Agmuḍ alemmas|wegmuḍ alemmas]]. Isem-agi yekka-d seg yisem wis sin n [[Yeɛqub]].

==Amezruy==

Deg lqern 19, akk d [[Theodor Herzl]] yexleq zionizem : udayen bɣan a d-uɣalen ɣer tmurt taneṣlit-nsen. Assmi kksen yingliziyen falsṭin seg ifassen n tterk, udayen zemren ad ruḥen ɣer falasṭin, uɣen-d akal seg weɛraben, bnan u zedɣen.

G 1984, [[Langliz]] teffeɣ-d seg falasṭin, l'ONU tegzem akal-agi di sin : 

*Tamurt n falasṭin ideg zedɣen 99% aɛraven.
*Tamurt n israyil ideg zedɣen 55% udayen.

Udayen qeblen, aɛraben ur qeblen ara lḥal-agi, 7 timura n weɛraben ttnaɣen akk d tmurt tamaynut n wudayen : Israyil terbeḥ lgirra, terbeḥ akal s waral n 28% kter n wayen i-ten-id-ifkan l'ONU. Kra n weɛraben i yellan deg Israyil rewlen, meɛna kra qqimen: tutlayt-nsen tutlayt tunṣibt. Akk udayen i yellan deg tamurt n falsṭin rewelen ɣer Israyil.

G 1967, maṣer tskker abrid n lebḥer n [[tiran]], ihi Israyil tebda lgirra amgal maṣer, timura n weɛraben nniḍen bɣan ad ɛawnen maṣer meɛna akk xesren, Israyil terbeḥ daɣen kter akal.

G 1973, aɛraben xeddmen lgirra tikkelt nniḍen akk d yisral, meɛna xesren daɣen : lgirra d wakal. Israyil tuɣal-d tameqqrant zdat Israyil n 1948.

